title: Ignorance is Death
itunes:title: Ignorance is Death
description:
Episode 561 - We have all heard the phrase "Ignorance is bliss" but is that really true? I honestly don't think that it is. I think that ignorance is the root of all our problems, so in this episode I will dive into this topic and talk about why knowledge is your key to the life you want.
